=========================================================================
=                               TMUX                                    =
=========================================================================

Session Management:
------------------
- tmux new -s session_name 
Creates new Session
- tmux attach -t session_name
Attach to a session
- tmux switch -t session_name
Switch b/w sessions
- tmux list-sessions (or) tmux ls
    List all session
- tmux detach (or) (prefix + d)
    Detach from the session

Windows:
-------
- tmux new-window (or) (prefix + c)
    Create new window in a session
- tmux select-window -t :0-9 (or) (prefix + 0-9)
    Toggle between the windows
    - prefix + n
    Toggel to the next window in the buffer
    - prefix + p
    Toggle to the previos window in the buffer
-tmux rename-window (or) (prefix + ,)
    Rename the window

Panes:
------
- tmux split-window (or) (prefix + â€œ)
    Split window Horizontally
- tmux split-window -h (or) (prefix + %)
    Split window vertically
